Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想夸大事实\NOkay, I don't want to overstate this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但这肯定是最棒的婚礼礼品袋了\Nbut these have to be the best wedding gift bags ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.22,0:00:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,根本比不上格温妮斯·帕特洛的婚礼\NIt's gonna be hard to beat Gwyneth Paltrow's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说他们送的是她的素描肖像\NI heard they gave away beautiful charcoal drawings of Gwyneth Paltrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信 Brooke竟然要结婚了\NI can't believe Brooke's getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从来没见过这位姓Elliot的家伙\NWe've never even met this Elliot guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信 Jane和Alex竟然有一个姐姐\NI can't believe Jane and Alex have an older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从没见过她 从没提起过她\NI mean, we never see her, never talk about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 从没在你们的闪回里出现过 - 闪回?\N- she never shows up in any of your flashbacks.- Flashbacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那是Jane和Alex照片集的名字\NThat's what Jane and Alex call their photo albums.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 Penny 只有照片集叫这名字的\NGod, Penny. Know what things are called for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 Brooke真的存在\NTrust me, Brooke is very real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她在香港有份理想的工作\NShe has a perfect job in Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她的头发有肉桂海滩的味道 她非常完美\NHer hair smells like a perfect beach made of cinnamon. She is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,作为伴娘 我想要这场婚礼...\NAnd as maid of honor, I need this wedding to be--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟我一起说 真...完美 - 珍...珠港\N- say it with me-- Perfect. - Pearl Harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,珍珠港 因为我们想让婚礼充满爆点\NPearl Harbor! 'Cause we want this wedding to be da bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就像迈克尔·贝的电影世界末日一样\NJust like that Michael Bay movie "Armageddon."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - Jane 你真心要疯啊\N- What? - Jane, you're acting extra nuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还不是把汤匙当茶匙的那种疯\Nand I'm not talking about "mistaking the teaspoon with the tablespoon" kinda nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是梅尔·吉布森喝下五小时能量饮料\NI'm talking about "Mel Gibson downing a 5-hour energy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然后不小心出现在受戒礼的那种疯\Nand by accident showing up at a Bar Mitzvah" kinda nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Brooke把Jane逼疯了 她比Jane还要Jane\NBrooke makes Jane crazy. She out-Janes Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在她面前 Jane也就是Alex的水平\NShe shows up, becomes the Jane, Jane gets bumped down to Alex's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我就只能做个宝宝\NAnd I just stay the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看Brooke给了我什么 让我不嫉妒她的戒指\NLook what Brooke got me so I wouldn't be jealous of her ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,戒指糖\NOh, a little suck candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,能被邀请 我就很开心\NI'm just glad I got invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直认识Brooke 而且仰慕她\NLike, I've known Brooke my whole life and looked up to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道 她竟然记得我\Nbut I didn't know that she would remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她不记得 你和Max是我带去的\NShe doesn't. You and Max are my plus-twos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.59,0:01:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你们得帮着客人泊车 - Jane\N- and you're gonna have to park some cars. - Jane!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 不会出问题的 好吗\NBabe, everything's gonna be fine, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我会一直陪在你身边\NI'll be right by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至允许你那种族歧视的侄子 问我认不认识Blair Underwood\NI'll even let your racist cousins ask me if I know Blair Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好像所有黑人都是朋友似的\NLike... like all black people are friends are somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 拜托\NI mean, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 真希望跟他做朋友\NGod, I wish I was friends with Blair Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的软陶珠子做好了\NMy clay beads are ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙想帮我制作几条项链吗\NHow many of you cool cats wanna help me crank out a few necklaces?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,额的神啊\NOhh! Oh, my goodness. Yes, oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我要制作一些聚合物...\NI'm working with some polymers right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我了个...\NHey. What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex 我看见你躲在那\NAlex, I can see you hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还能看见我吗\NCan you still see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 看得更清楚了\NYes. Even more now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NFine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这次已经好多了\NNice try, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以...\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咱什么时候告诉大家这件事\NWhen are we gonna tell everybody about the thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\NWhat thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们如何分手的事\NThe thing about how we broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 那件事\NOh, right. That thing.
