Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE5F629&}幸福终点站 第三季 第23集\N<font color=#29F6E5>Happy.Endings.S03E23</font>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就真的发生了\NSo this is really happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们分手了\NWe're breaking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,当你像这样大声说出来时 就都明白了\NYeah, when you say it out loud like that, it just really sinks in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我发现绯闻女孩其实是男的\NLike when I found out Gossip Girl was a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,完全同意\NTotally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们都同意哈 在你姐结婚前不告诉任何人\NSo we both agree, we don't tell everyone until after your sister's wedding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 肯定会让大家心烦意乱\NYeah, it would be too much of a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我的家人特别爱八卦 他们还总会错意\NPlus, my family is so gossipy and they always get the story wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,记得吗 有一次你说你喜欢西尼德·玛丽\NRemember that one time you said you like Sinead O'Connor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,当消息传了一圈回来时 变成了你在一所女子学院教巫术\Nand by the time it got back to us, you were teaching Wicca at a women's college?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就告诉过你一个人 - 确实是\N- You were the only one that I told. - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,力量 勇气 镇静 不发牢骚\NStrength, courage, composure, no carbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\NHere we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Brooke - Jane\N- Hi, Brooke. - Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 欢迎来我家 - 谢谢\N- Welcome to my home! - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你肯定就是黑色Elliot了 - 黑色Elliot\N- And you must be Black... Elliot. - Black Elliot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只是外号哈 我们不会再说了\NYes. That's just a nickname that we'll stop using immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你邀请我们来你家 Jane\NThank you for having us to your home, Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你翻新过了吗\NHave you been renovating?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为所有地方都好像有一小层灰\NBecause it looks like everything's covered with a thin layer of dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,眼神不错\NGood catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定是彻底打扫过了 而不是被迫随便搞搞的\NYeah, I must've just cleaned thoroughly instead of compulsively.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Brooke - 你好\N- Brooke! - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给我一些爱 姑娘 - 很高兴见到你\N- Gimme some love, girl. - Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\NSo good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你带把什么带回家了\NAnd look what you brought home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一位Elliot\NAn Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大家好 - 嗨\N- Hello, everyone. - Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 最终 另外一位Elliot - 是的\N- Ah. Finally, another Elliot. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这两年来 我都没跟其他叫Elliot的人玩\NI haven't hung out with another Elliot in, like, two years, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,抱一个\NBring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗 他闻上去也很像叫Elliot的人\NYou know, he even smells like an Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这真好\NYeah, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伙计 - 什么\N- Hey, yo, E. - Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我可以问你一个问题吗 - 什么\N- Can I ask you a question, man? - What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以问你一个小问题吗\NCan I ask you a little somethin' somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请说\NPlease do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们不在周围 我们说什么\NWhat we be sayin' when they ain't around?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 如果他们不在周围 我们会说什么\NI said, I said... what we be sayin' when they ain't around?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,白人很疯狂吗\NWhite people be crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah, they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你懂\NAah! I knew you gon' know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们的确很疯狂\NThey do be crazy, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只是一些人 - 都疯狂\N- Some do. - Y'all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们去喝点东西吧 我的Elliot - 我同意\N- Yeah, let's get you a drink, my Elliot. - All right, I'm with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Brooke - 妹妹\N- Brooke! - Little sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真高兴\NOh, it's so good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我带了什么\NWhat'd you bring me? What'd you bring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,中国糯米糖 包装纸可以吃\NChinese rice candy. You can eat the wrapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好节省时间哦\NThat'll save me so much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我爱你 姐姐 - 我也爱你\N- I love you, sis. - I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 姑娘 - 嗨\N- Hey, girl! - Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 我是Brooke Kerkovich 这是...\NUh, hi, I'm Brooke Kerkovich. It's an...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 好的\NHi. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Brooke 我是Penny Hartz\NBrooke, Penny Hartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常在你家过夜\NI slept over at your house a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,七年级时 我写过一篇关于你的文章\NOh, I wrote that paper on you in seventh grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你开车撞我 整个夏天我腿都绑着绷带\NYou hit me with your car, and I had to wear a leg brace all summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 是哪条腿来着\NOh, yes. That's right. What leg was that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,左腿\NThe left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我以为是另外一个人\NNo. Sorry, I'm thinking of someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NYeah, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我也以为是另外一个人\NYeah, I was thinking of someone else, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多金发\NSo much blonde.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 坐下\NCome on. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她这人很古怪 - 是的\N- She's an odd one. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你和爸爸谈过了吗\NSo have you talked to dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信 他竟然食言了\NI can't believe he threw his back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他没法来 他不会参加婚礼的\NHe's immobilized. He's not coming to the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们要延期吗 - 延期? 都到这时候了?\N- Should we postpone? - Postpone? At this stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jane 你在开玩笑吧 - 是的\N- Jane, is that a joke? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,晚宴彩排计划是什么\NSo... how are the rehearsal dinner plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好 所有事情都按你的计划进行\NPerfect. Everything is done to your specifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈妈坐哪里 - 远离乐队的地方\N- Where's mom sitting? - Away from the band,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那她就不会试图加入乐队唱歌了\Nso she doesn't try to join them for a song.
