Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 我们懂了 你辅修了黑人历史\NDude, we get it. You minored in black history.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,非裔美国人学\NAfro-American studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你说辅修(minor) 简直太不礼貌了 (minor也有少数人种的意思)\NAnd I am offended by your use of the term "minor."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不是来这套的时候\NNow is not the time, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 Berg医生 我知道咱家的孩子都是你接生的\NAll right, Dr. Berg, I know you delivered every child in this family,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是您坐错位置了\Nbut you're in the wrong seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望您能像George Clinton那样 从这里走开\NSo I'm gonna need you to make like George Clinton and get the funk outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jane - 怎么了\N- Jane. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛跟B医生过不去\NWhy are you freaking out on Dr. B?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为座位表弄坏了 所以每个人都坐错了位置\NBecause I put everyone in the wrong place because the seating chart is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 我把座位表去了模\N- What? - I had to unlaminate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就满身大汗 只有Brooke来的时候我才这样\Nand then I got those weird sweats that I only get when Brooke's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怪不得妈跑到乐队那边去了\NWell, that explains why mom ended up by the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看来座位完全乱了套\NSo... the seating is a complete mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得那女人根本不该出现在这里\Nand I'm pretty sure that woman doesn't even belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次用卫生棉 就是你给买的\NYou bought me my first maxi pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane 我很清楚你现在压力过大\NJane, it's very clear to me that the pressure is getting to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得还是给你安排一个简单点的工作\Nand I think we need to give you a simpler task.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,放手 放手\NLet go. Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你明天不用帮我准备了\NInstead of helping me get ready tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是去发节目单好了\NI think it would be better if you handed out programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 至于你... - 啊?\N- And you... - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你表现得很不错\Nare doing a wonderful job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你...安排得不错\NY-you-- yeah, that's a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,冒昧问下 你还好吗\NAw, I'm sorry. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 挺好的 - 那就好\N- I'm good. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的挺好 其实我要去查看一下\NI'm really good. Yeah. I gotta-- actually, I gotta check on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那行 - 那边一些事\N- Okay. - The... thing in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好了哟 大块头 挪挪地方\NAll right. Okay, big boy, let's go. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 Elliot认识Blair Underwood\NAre you serious? Elliot knows Blair Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 他还很喜欢别人问起这事\NOh, yeah. And he loves it when people ask him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了\NHere he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Elliot 你认识Blair Underwood吗\NHey, Elliot. You know Blair Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么\NWhat? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\NOh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,难道所有黑人都认识Blair Underwood吗\NLike all black people are just supposed to know Blair Underwood, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 我确实认识Blair\Nactually, I do know Blair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他人非常好 是我们慈善机构的发言人\NHe's a great guy. He's a spokesman for a charity I work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这可太牛了 Elliot\NWow! That is very impressive, Elliot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有不少故事可以讲讲吧\NThe stories you must have, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么 不能这样\NWhat? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都是些蠢事 我才是牛人\NThe-- stories are stupid! I'm impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Jackie Robinson\NI'm Jackie Robinson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alex...怎么喝酒呢\NSo, Alex... drinking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑到你现在的情况 是不是不太...\NIn your condition? Isn't that--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这在欧洲还是很合适的吧 是的\NUh, acceptable in Europe? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你带着浓浓的法式风情 Alex - 说得没错\N- How very French of you, Alex. - I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, la la! Pepe le pew! French Stewart!\NOoh, la la! Pepe le pew! French Stewart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alex 胃口怎么样  - 好到爆\NAnd, Alex, how are your cravings? Insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好到爆 谢谢问候\NTotally insane. Thank you for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是少见\Nthis rarely happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我总觉得错过了什么\NI feel like I'm missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是那时 人们突然对亚麻裤着迷\NLike that time that everybody turned on linen pants all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没没 我不觉得\NNo. No. No. No, I don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们该怎么办\NOkay, what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得再次改变新闻导向\NWe need to change the news cycle again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有办法了\NI have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来一下 Sher\NScuttle your butt on over here, Sher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有一条顶级八卦 但你不能说出去 行吗\NI got some grade-A goss, but you have it keep it a secret. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jane和Brad正闹分手\NJane and Brad are on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白我的意思了吗\NYou tastin' what I'm wastin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pen 别说了 - 只是别告诉任何人\N- Pen, come on. - Just... just don't tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,保证守口如瓶\NOh! Your secret's safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这招可要奏效啊 Max\NThis better work, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,耐心等待\NGive it time. Give it time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 跟你们透露一个秘密\NSo this is hush-hush,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Brad有私生子了 所以Brad和Jane正闹离婚\Nbut Brad and Jane are divorcing because Brad has a love child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,传播得真快\NWow. That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,流言蜚语满天飞呀\NThey really took it and ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,添油加醋 不胫而走\NYeah, but you know what I liked? They really made it their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要折叠 那不是垃圾\NDo not fold that! It's not garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是下午精彩活动的介绍指南\NIt's a guide to your magical afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Brooke听说 你好像对来宾不太友善\NHey, um, so Brooke heard that you were making people feel uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她打算直接把册子放桌子上\NSo she thought it'd be better if you just let the podium do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放桌子上 - 不好意思 我只是...\N- The podium? - Sorry, Jane. I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只是运气好\NI lucked out that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我天生就是做撒花女的份 - 是啊...\N- I was born for this whole flower girl gig. - Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,撒花的时机和方式都太不靠谱了\NIt's not at all how or when you're supposed to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Brooke女士 Elliot先生 重要时刻到了\NBrooke, Elliot, we've reached the big moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Elliot 你愿意Brooke成为你的妻子吗\NElliot, do you take Brooke to be your lawfully wedded wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我愿意 - 不要 不要\N- I do. - Ohh. No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Brooke 你愿意让Elliot成为你的丈夫吗\NAnd do you, Brooke, take Elliot to be... your lawfully wedded husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要 - 什么\N- No! - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 不是说它们 起火了\NNo, no, not them. There is a fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,手册着火了\Nand... programs are on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在这别动 我是消防志愿者\NEveryone stay here. I'm a volunteer firefighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是消防志愿者\NI'm a volunteer firefighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,继续炫耀你的工作经历吧 老兄\NKeep reading us your resume, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dave 带Alex出去\NDave, get Alex out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,烟雾对小孩子不好\NThe fumes are bad for the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在家里 我确实算小孩子 但我是成年人\NI know I'm the baby of the family, but I'm a big girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我能走出玉米迷宫 逃出这里更不在话下\NIf I can get through a corn maze, I can get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我是说你肚子里怀的宝宝\NNo, the baby you're having.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 什么\N- What? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是的 Brad和Jane才有宝宝了 - 什么\N- No, it's Brad and Jane that are having the baby. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 那是Brad和某女人的野种\NNo! It's a love child that Brad has with some floozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以他们才闹离婚的 - 什么\N- That's why they're getting divorced. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 我哪有什么私生子\N- What? - I'm not having a love child!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那究竟是谁分手了\NWell, then who's breaking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是我跟Dave - 什么\N- Dave and I are. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我本该早告诉你们\NI know. I... We should've told all of you sooner, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但其他谣言 我毫不知情\NI have no idea where these other stories came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Max和Penny告诉我们的\NMax and Penny told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这样啊 - 那就对了\N- Okay, well... - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是情非得已 必须改变新闻导向\NLook, I'm sorry. I had to change the news cycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我告诉大家Penny已经53岁了\Nlike how I told everyone Penny was 53.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 大家都不惊讶吗\NOh, come on! No gasps on that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那我在厕所听说有人怀宝宝 什么情况\NWell, then who did I overhear talking about a baby in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是Kerkovich家的女儿\NI know it's a Kerkovich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是我 - 不是我\N- It wasn't me. - It was not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 行了吧\NIt's me. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀孕了\NI'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Brooke 婚礼太赞了\NBrooke, the ceremony was lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,您是哪位\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NHow you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,奉子成婚 还伴有瓢泼大雨\NWell, my shotgun wedding got soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道在你心中 我是完美的\NLook, I know you think I'm perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但实际上 我并非完人\Nbut I'm actually not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 高兴了吧 - 不高兴\N- Happy? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,高兴 很高兴\NYes. Very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来 我对你很苛刻\NI know I've always been a little bit hard on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是因为 我觉得你很有潜力\Nbut it's because I knew how much potential you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你可以很优秀\NI knew you could be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至可能比我还优秀\NMaybe even better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我以前会打击你\NThat's why I had to destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:18:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你对我说过最中听的话了\NThat is the nicest thing you have ever said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,实话实说\NWell, you deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你还只是稍稍毁了我的婚礼\NPlus, you only sort of ruined my wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,毁了我婚礼的是Max和Penny\NMax and Penny really ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她记得我的名字 太棒了\NShe remembered me! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一句 真为你感到高兴\NAgain, I'm so happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 E - 兄弟\N- Hey, yo, E. - Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我只是想让你知道\Nlisten, I just wanna let you know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你要加入我们家庭\Nthat I'm really happy to have you in the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了\NOh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是家里的第一个黑汉子 确实为我铺了路\NAnd look, I know you being here first did make it easier for me.
